        <updateDate>2016-02-19T22:05:58Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>21st Century Visa Vetting Act</strong></p> <p>This bill authorizes the Department of Homeland Security to search open source information, including Internet sites and social media postings, of an alien who applies for a visa to enter the United States to determine if the alien is inadmissible under the Immigration and Nationality Act.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
